items.name: HelpURL
lines: provides a help URL to be associated with a category

items.name: ProgrammaticName
lines: contains the programmatic name of the category.

This programmatic name is used internally: XPropertyHandler::describePropertyLine() sets a programmatic category name at LineDescriptor::Category, and an object inspector uses this to find the proper PropertyCategoryDescriptor.

items.name: UIName
lines: provides a human-readable name (which can be presented at the UI) for a category.
